Package com.dataartisans.flinktraining.exercises.datastream_java.connectors

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PopularPlacesFromKafka
    Java reference implementation for the "Popular Places" exercise of the Flink training (http://dataartisans.github.io/flink-training).
    PopularPlacesFromKafka.GridCellMatcher
    Maps taxi ride to grid cell and event type.
    PopularPlacesFromKafka.GridToCoordinates
    Maps the grid cell id back to longitude and latitude coordinates.
    PopularPlacesFromKafka.RideCounter
    Counts the number of rides arriving or departing.
    PopularPlacesFromKafka.TaxiRideTSExtractor
    Assigns timestamps to TaxiRide records.
    PopularPlacesToES
    Java reference implementation for the "Popular Places" exercise of the Flink training (http://dataartisans.github.io/flink-training).
    PopularPlacesToES.GridCellMatcher
    Maps taxi ride to grid cell and event type.
    PopularPlacesToES.GridToCoordinates
    Maps the grid cell id back to longitude and latitude coordinates.
    PopularPlacesToES.PopularPlaceInserter
    Inserts popular places into the "nyc-places" index.
    PopularPlacesToES.RideCounter
    Counts the number of rides arriving or departing.
    RideCleansingToKafka
    Java reference implementation for the "Ride Cleansing" exercise of the Flink training (http://dataartisans.github.io/flink-training).
